01:17:06,188 --> 01:17:08,490
Well, she's finally asleep.

01:17:09,891 --> 01:17:11,827
It's all your fault.

01:17:11,860 --> 01:17:14,396
You don't know how
to make a man happy

01:17:14,429 --> 01:17:16,431
and now my son has gone crazy.

01:17:16,465 --> 01:17:18,300
