like this.

01:17:32,914 --> 01:17:35,784
I've had it.
I have had it.

01:17:37,152 --> 01:17:39,855
The marriage is over.

01:17:39,888 --> 01:17:44,726
Anna, don't throw anything
away until you have
looked inside.

01:17:45,527 --> 01:17:48,196
Mama, I know what I saw.

01:17:48,730 --> 01:17:50,165
You lie, Anna.

01:17:51,299 --> 01:17:52,634
Tell me you lie.

01:17:54,202 --> 01:17:57,773
