01:17:57,806 --> 01:18:01,543
-Look, why don't we all
just...
-Shut up, shut up!

01:18:01,576 --> 01:18:05,480
-I don't want to hear nothing.
-Hmm, you never do.

01:18:05,514 --> 01:18:09,084
Father Martino
called again, mmm?

01:18:09,117 --> 01:18:14,556
I tell you, I don't
wanna talk to him.
He don't help me.

01:18:14,589 --> 01:18:16,224
(WHISPERS)
Nobody must know.

01:18:18,193 --> 01:18:20,295
Where's my son?

01:18:20,328 --> 01:18:22,564
-He's probably with his lover.
-(NINA GASPS)

01:18:23,765 --> 01:18:27,636
Anna, please, everybody's
in pain. Stop.

01:18:27,669 --> 01:18:31,807
-You see, what happened to
my family since they come?
-Putanas.

01:18:32,874 --> 01:18:34,676
Diavolo!
(SPITTING)

01:18:37,345 --> 01:18:39,648
