put a curse on him.

01:18:39,681 --> 01:18:43,452
Oh poor  sorella, poor Nina.

01:18:43,485 --> 01:18:48,156
Anna, find out what is really
going on with your husband.

01:18:48,190 --> 01:18:50,392
Don't give up so easily.

01:18:50,425 --> 01:18:53,495
Cara, per favore,
do it for Joanne, huh?

01:18:53,528 --> 01:18:58,033
