that's our specialty.

01:20:07,803 --> 01:20:09,805
(I'LL BE HOME FOR CHRISTMAS
PLAYING)

01:21:43,465 --> 01:21:45,200
Anna, let me explain,

01:21:45,934 --> 01:21:47,402
it's not what you think.

01:21:49,070 --> 01:21:52,140
Anna, Anna.

01:22:06,755 --> 01:22:09,858
I wish for peace for everybody
in this New Year.

01:22:15,830 --> 01:22:17,332
I don't know what to say.

01:22:21,102 --> 01:22:22,771
I don't have anything to give.

01:22:32,147 --> 01:22:33,715
Nardo.

01:22:45,527 --> 01:22:48,096
So, are you finished
with penance?

01:22:48,129 --> 01:22:50,966
My penance is only over
when Anna takes me back.

01:22:50,999 --> 01:22:55,870
Oh, Nardo, Anna cannot
take you back
unless you talk to her.

01:22:57,706 --> 01:22:59,607
She doesn't want
to talk to me.

01:22:59,641 --> 01:23:01,643
How do you know this?

01:23:01,676 --> 01:23:04,346
-I saw it.
-What? You saw what? What?

01:23:05,547 --> 01:23:07,916
Blank. Hate.

01:23:08,583 --> 01:23:10,986
Oh, you saw pain.

01:23:11,019 --> 01:23:13,688
You saw a woman
who feels betrayed.

01:23:13,722 --> 01:23:16,324
Nardo,
you've got to talk to her.

01:23:16,358 --> 01:23:17,959
She loves you.

01:23:19,361 --> 01:23:20,462
I love her.

01:23:20,495 --> 01:23:23,198
Well, then you must
talk to her.

01:23:23,231 --> 01:23:26,301
Show her that
you're no longer a boy.

01:23:26,334 --> 01:23:28,870
That you are a changed man.

01:23:28,903 --> 01:23:32,607
I mean, I do not see the point
of you standing here in a
church feeling guilty

01:23:32,640 --> 01:23:34,342
and feeling bad.
What's the point?

01:23:35,377 --> 01:23:37,145
What should I do?

01:23:37,178 --> 01:23:40,048
Well, first of all,
clean yourself up

01:23:40,081 --> 01:23:42,884
you look disgusting,
like a bum from the street.

01:23:44,719 --> 01:23:47,856
Look, this is for your life.

01:23:47,889 --> 01:23:51,026
It is not for poker,
you understand me?
No poker.

01:23:51,059 --> 01:23:53,128
-Understand?
-I understand.

01:23:53,161 --> 01:23:54,929
All right. Do you swear?

01:23:58,099 --> 01:23:59,501
I swear to God.

01:24:01,002 --> 01:24:02,670
Do you swear on your baby?

01:24:05,040 --> 01:24:06,875
I swear on my baby.

01:24:09,077 --> 01:24:11,112
