a second chance.

01:27:22,103 --> 01:27:24,806
-But I need you to back me up.
-Back you up?

01:27:26,407 --> 01:27:29,244
Now, that means that things
are gonna have to change.

01:27:31,779 --> 01:27:38,086
Now, I never wanna hear you
say one word

01:27:38,119 --> 01:27:40,555
against my wife

01:27:40,588 --> 01:27:43,524
-or her mother again.
-Leonardo...

01:27:43,558 --> 01:27:47,028
Mama, not one word,

01:27:47,061 --> 01:27:50,365
do you understand? Do you?

01:27:52,500 --> 01:27:53,501
NINA:  Si.

01:27:55,370 --> 01:27:58,573
Anna, everybody
makes mistakes in life.

01:28:00,041 --> 01:28:01,609
Nardo loves you.

01:28:02,944 --> 01:28:04,579
And I know you love him, too.

01:28:06,814 --> 01:28:08,483
Daddy, daddy.

01:28:10,084 --> 01:28:11,419
